<HEADLINE>
<P>
PREP BASEBALL '94: EMPIRE LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Loara 
</P>
<P>
 1993 RECORDS: 
</P>
<P>
 OVERALL: 3-20 
</P>
