 COACH: David Lappin 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 3-20 04,20,05,07,05 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T Mike 
Boomsma Sr. 1B/P R-L Ean Brown Sr. 3B/OF R-R Chris Carrillo Sr. 2B R-R Carson 
