 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 244-89-4 04,20,05,06,05 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T 
Jason Murrietta Sr. C R-R Jason Webb Jr. 3B R-R 04,16,05,06,05 TOP RETURNERS 
YR. POS. B-T Scott Hild Sr. P R-R Joe Quezada Sr. 2B L-R Jeremy Viscusi Sr. OF 
