<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: HOMEBASE'S ORR WILL OVERSEE COMPANY INFORMATION 
SYSTEMS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jim Orr has been promoted to vice president/management information systems for 
HomeBase Inc., the Irvine-based home improvement warehouse chain. Orr, who was 
formerly data center director for the 83-store chain, will oversee data center 
operations, distributed systems, and telecommunications and systems 
development. Orr joined HomeBase in 1988 as manager of computer operations. 
</P>
