<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 David E. Limebrook has been appointed vice president, tactical marketing, for 
Times Mirror Cable Television in Irvine.He was formerly marketing director. 
Limebrook joined the company in 1980 as a sales representative in the San Diego 
system. He was later named manager, national direct sales and director, group 
marketing and sales, before moving to the Orange County system in 1987. In 
addition, Eric P. Brown has joined the company as vice president, strategic 
marketing. He was previously with Cabason Inc., a San Diego management 
consulting firm he founded. Before that, Brown was vice president of product 
management at Bumble Bee Seafoods Inc. 
</P>
