<P>
Play Review; Infobox 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA030394-0177 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 019032 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 3, 1994, Thursday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Ventura County Life; Part J; Page 4 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
