</P>
<P>
 On the Cover 
</P>
<P>
 Long Beach activist Betsy Bredau shows some of the materials she uses in 
teaching neighborhood associations how to sue landlords in Small Claims Court 
to get them to clean up drug-plagued properties--a tactic she has used 
successfully to improve conditions in her own neighborhood. 
</P>
