<P>
 Museum -- A photograph in Tuesday's editions of The Times appeared to identify 
a Bank of America building as the future site of the Museum of Television and 
Radio. The museum actually will be housed in a former bank building at 469 
Beverly Drive that was in the foreground of the photograph. 
